{"id": 1946, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你都是怎么边玩游戏边交朋友的？", "description": "谁说游戏宅都是社交无能，我玩游戏认识的小伙伴比你走过的桥都多。", "record_count": 4357, "comment_count": 53, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171006174547NYQgKutdPsoOV2zm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-08T17:00:02Z", "questions": [{"id": 3091, "title": "现如今，你都是怎么边玩游戏边交朋友的？", "content": "现如今，你都是怎么边玩游戏边交朋友的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 240400, "content": "和现实好友一起绝地求生，一边对骂一边互相扶持", "image": "img/option/option/20171006181722J9yhMcvHpq1Pgud5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240401, "content": "有时候聚会的由头就是为了要聚众王者荣耀", "image": "img/option/option/20171006181734jkwNB23SqCOY18nt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240402, "content": "恭敬地请朋友中的王者带自己排位", "image": "img/option/option/20171006181811QLGAu6myIEqJ48Kg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240403, "content": "线上狼人杀、阿瓦隆，语音唠嗑认识了有趣的小伙伴", "image": "img/option/option/20171006182304U6odgL8WufCTavBO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240404, "content": "玩球球大作战之类的 io 游戏，和队友互相关注", "image": "img/option/option/20171006181847VG1mBxDviteIMCo5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240405, "content": "因为玩 Ingress、Pokémon GO ，出门结识不少同好", "image": "img/option/option/20171006181921kyvs24Z1SAF0ngPp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240406, "content": "通过传统的师徒、婚姻、战队系统在游戏里交朋友", "image": "img/option/option/20171006181934vZFkGJC04Ew1WpTR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240407, "content": "通过GameCenter、Steam等游戏平台认识其他玩家", "image": "img/option/option/20171006181951IDFnYUugBJ85fCTX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240408, "content": "蚂蚁森林偷能量蚂蚁庄园赶鸡，和支付宝好友互动", "image": "img/option/option/20171006182003qsiIlcVxmF3HTzvG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240409, "content": "聚餐等饭上桌的时候玩谁是卧底之类的休闲游戏", "image": "img/option/option/201710061820346zWDsahdIZyOwpE0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240613, "content": "邀请朋友来家一起玩主机游戏，顺便共享游戏碟", "image": "img/option/option/20171009105915DX5i7vcMn8UApkgw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}